      <title>ASML 在华销售激增凸显美国加强限制的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/asml-s-surging-china-sales-underscore-us-threat-of-tighter-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿斯利康第二季度对华销售额激增，占该公司总收入的近一半，这表明在拜登政府考虑采取更严厉的限制措施之际，美国出口限制的影响有限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/asml-s-surging-china-sales-underscore-us-threat-of-tighter-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:25:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
